     H            Y.
     F** AB#RW5 ------------------------------------------------------
     F*  CREATE DATA IN AU#PP10 FROM AB#PP10
     F*      IN CASE APICS PROCESS FAILED INBETWEEN AB#PP10 AND AU#PP11
     F*
     F*  AB#0207 = MADE FROM AB#PP10 BY QRY
     F*     SELECTION: KOYY,KOMM,KODD,KOME='EDI',NONY
     F*
     F*  AB#WP202 = CREATED IN QTEMP(OR IN TEST LIBRARY)
     F*
     F*  AFTER THIS PGM RUN, RUN AB#R21 (CREATE DATA IN AB#WP20),
     F*                 THEN RUN AB#R2J (CREATE DATA IN AU#PP11).
     F*
     F*  NOTES:
     F*    (1) MAKE SURE THE LIBRARY LIST.
     F*    (2) MAKE SURE THAT AU#PP11, AN#PP11 ARE IN WHICH LIBRARY.
     F*        AN#PP11 SHOULD HAVE THE CURRENT DATA.
     F*
     F*---------------------------- AB#RW5 --------------------------
%0001FAB#0207 IP  E                    DISK
     F            AB#0207                           KRENAMEAB#02R
%0001FAB#WP202O   F     256            DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 BAMHIN
     I                                        1   5 BAMHN1
     I                                        6  10 BAMHN2
     I                                       11  15 BAMHN3
     I                                       16  20 BAMHN4
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 BASHIN
     I                                        1   5 BASHN1
     I                                        6  10 BASHN2
     I                                       11  12 BASHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BANOHZ
     I                                        1   40BANOYY
     I                                        5   60BANOMM
     I                                        7   80BANODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BAURHZ
     I                                        1   40BAURYY
     I                                        5   60BAURMM
     I                                        7   80BAURDD
      *-----------------------------------------------
     C                     EXCPTDT
      *-----------------------------------------------
      *
     OAB#WP202E                DT
     O                         BASIRE     4
     O                         BASIRK     5
     O                         BATOKU     9
